snippet.title: Steel Titan Gameplay Trailer - Releasing October 2023
snippet.description:
In this video, we're taking a look at Steel Titan, the new Mech game coming out in October! Follow us on Twitter and Itch for more updates!

Itch.io: https://raptorgamedev.itch.io/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RaptorGameDev
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/Steel-Titan/833960

If you're a fan of mech games, then you'll definitely want to check out Steel Titan. This third person shooter is set in a futuristic world full of action and adventure. Steel Titan is coming out in October and it's sure to be a hit!
